      "body" : "We don't currently reliably know when we're not in sync, unless it's so far back that it's before the highest checkpoint. The median measure is absolutely unacceptable for this kind of usage: doing that would allow a greifer to spin up a bunch of height lying nodes and block all  (with fee?) transactions.",
